📈 Philosophy
This tracker is built on the principle that consistency beats perfection. The goal isn't to never fail, but to build sustainable systems that help you improve over time. Small, consistent actions compound into significant life changes.

Built with ❤️ for anyone looking to build better habits and break free from the ones holding them back.
